M|pre-mortem|- Klein, G. (2007). "Performing a Project Premortem." Harvard Business rv.
M|pre-mortem|- Mitchell, D. J., et al. (1989). "Back to the Future: Temporal Perspective in the Explanation of Events." Journal of Behavioral dec Making.